						               													<description>Edward De Bono's &amp;quot;Mind Pack&amp;quot; has a book (Mind Power) and a package of pieces that are used to play over 80 games and exercises to help with thinking more efficiently, creatively and have greater concentration. This product teaches 'lateral thinking' techniques.  This is taking familiar ideas and associations and redefining them to make everyday thinking enjoyable.  It also includes his famous Six Hats thinking technique, which uses role-playing to help you realize your full mind power.  The Mind Pack package comes with two sheets of gaming tokens, a gaming board and three decks of specialized cards.  All of these pieces, plus the creative thinking ideas within the book itself can lead one to developing and exploring board game creation in directions not previously explored.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
